snippet.title: Bleach: Rebirth of Souls - Trailer | TGS 2024
snippet.description:
Check out the stylish anime action of Bleach: Rebirth of Souls in this trailer from Tokyo Game Show. The game is coming to Xbox consoles in early 2025.
